T|15 ·|0|The drag-and-drop calendar where approved posts land. Place posts across days/weeks to keep every platform's posting frequency fully active.
T|15 ·|1|
T|Purp|0|"Schedule across every platform … a card → a slot → publishing operations center on a calendar." A powerful drag-and-drop posting calendar so the owner can ensure their posting frequency is met across all platforms. Approved posts (from sl Approvals/Shorts) show up here and can be dragged into day/time slots.
T|Purp|1|
T|Page|0|Title: Scheduler, breadcrumb Vibe w/ AI / Scheduler.
T|Page|1|Sub-line: "Schedule across every platform … publishing operations center."
T|Page|2|Platform filter chips: All platforms, YouTube, LinkedIn, Instagram, TikTok.
T|Page|3|Buttons: Refine and Schedule nx slot.
T|Page|4|
T|Cale|0|A week/day calendar (columns are days, e.g. 18–24) populated w/ post cards in time slots.
T|Cale|1|Cards show the platform, the post (e.g. "Convert the ag tn," "Shipping software in 20 min," "Memory sy breakdown") and time.
T|Cale|2|Drag and drop to move a post to a different day/slot — the core interaction — so the schedule can be balanced and gaps filled to meet frequency targets.
T|Cale|3|
T|Righ|0|fl triage — surfaces posts that failed to publish (e.g. "A post that didn't go: needs the ap auth … re-auth"), w/ Diagnose and cr fix task actions, and a Reauthorize button. Keeps the posting engine healthy.
T|Righ|1|Publishing engine — status of the auto-publishing sy, connected accounts, nx scheduled post, and queue health.
T|Righ|2|
T|Work|0|sl Approvals / Shorts "Schedule" → card appears in Scheduler → owner drags into the desired day/time → publishing engine posts automatically at the slot → failures surface in fl triage for a quick fix → perf flows to sl an (16).